<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=102827826931435></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f102827826931435><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=2&mid=102827826931435>RE: secondary</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=2&mid=102827826931435#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=147660><span id= >Tactikal</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>76 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Aug 2nd 5:04 AM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[2.79]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>If I were you, I would try and keep up on all my melee skills.&nbsp;&nbsp;I used 1hs, 1hp, 1hb all throughout the game (currently using 2 piercers).  I think my 1st set of weapons was a harpoon of the depths and light velium sword.  And as I leveled I kept up my 1hs and 1hp combo often enough to where I havent used 1hs in like almost 10 levels and it is still at a point to where i could use it reliably.  However 1hb was completely neglected until I hit lvl 53 or so and I had to spend a lot of time beating on other peoples mobs to get my skill up to where I could use it for real (only reason I even worked it up was cuz I thought I was going to be getting a &quot;Dain Hammer&quot; [tri plated golden hackle hammer sp?]).  But then I didnt and wound up using a Guard Captains Mallet I won in a group anyways. <br><br>Anyways, aside from my rambling, my point is that you should try and keep all your skills up no matter what.  You never know what kind of weapon your going to get your hands on, and it sux to not be able to use it effectively in a group because you dont have the skill nessecary to hit with it. <br>&nbsp;<br>~Tactikal Mizkalculation~&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>60 ASSASSIN <br>Cruxor Thunderblade<br>Level 51 gimp Paladin<br>Vazaelle<br></td></tr>
