	   <tr><td colspan=2>Bellow lvl 50 your 1hb and 1hs cap at 200 (at lvl 39) while your piercing caps at 210 (at lvl 41), so for a while, at least, you are probably going to want equip two piercers (correct spelling?).&nbsp;&nbsp;Having said that, I would recommend that you keep all your melee skills maxed ((lvl + 1)*5), as several others have all ready stated, you don't want to restrict your choice of weapons later on.<br><br>You might want to get some low delay weapons to use to train your melee skills. While you are waiting for a spot in groups you can pull out your practice weapons and assist the group (ask first). Good weapons to use are things like the Kerran Fishing Pole (17 delay, 3 dmg, 1hb) or Gnoll Hide Lariat (20 delay, 3 dmg, proc stun, 1hs) which are cheap or not to hard to get (the lariats seem to go for &gt; 5pp in the bazaar, and the pole can be quested at lvl 18).    <br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
