	   <tr><td colspan=2>Grimling Picks are hardly up for sale cause most folks who get them from the grimlings in Tenebrous Mts see that they are not magic, assume they are junk, and dump them on vendors in Katta Kastellum or let them rot on the corpse.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br><br>If you can sneak+hide through Fungus Grove (rogue sneak+hide combo works great there even though its a 50+ zone) to Twilight Sea and then into Katta Katellum you can vendor mine.  Chances are you will find one for a couple of plat.<br><br>Most of the 11+ damage piercers (other than the pick) for sale are over 2500pp on my server, if they are for sale at all. They are so hard to get to or are no drop.  Some of the newest ones require a level of 45 to use.<br><br>I am level 43 now and use the SGMP most of the time. When I need a magic piercer in the primary (against higher level undead for example) I use a Crystal Grinder (9dmg/27dly AC 2) which I have had since I was level 19.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
