	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hail and well met fellow Rogues!&nbsp;&nbsp;After seeing a few posts here about pickpocketing Tani N' Mar, I thought I might pass on my first-hand experience on it.  First, check your pick-pocket skill - at about 190 or more - I do not believe Tani or Founy aggro anymore (unless I got really lucky on both)  - because when my skill was lower (185) Founy always aggroed on me.  I noticed also that I was not KOS to the Ebon Hand folks with DE Illusion - just aprehensive - which was a pleasant surprise (half-elven here). Anyhow, thought I'd pass on the tidbits of info - also there is an excellent guide to ragebringer on the web - <a href="http://www.matt.waggoner.com/ragebringer.html" target=_new>http://www.matt.waggoner.com/ragebringer.html</a><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
