	   <tr><td colspan=2>Ok I am planning on making a Rouge and I decided that my race is going to be a dwarf, I basically aiming for huge damage backstabs, so the extra strength would help, also it seems like most of everyone who is a Rouge is a Halfling so i figured i would be different. I was originally planning on making the character on Sullon or Vallon Zek, yet i have heard from quite a few people that Rouges suck at PVP. Any thoughts?<br>&nbsp;<br>------------------------<br>Macando 31 Human Wizard<br>Mazzik 23 Kat Beastie<br>Zellin 13 High Elf Cleric<br>Legends (Stormhammer) server<br>Riders of Kunark<br></td></tr>
