 dirk for a crescent blades of luclin I have 2k to my name ... so only 40k to go, unless i get lucky and catch lodizal. <br><br>Oh well guess i will get off my soap box, sorry watching a movie while i type this.  oh yea, and as far as pick pocketing Tani, I have hear tale of a way that you can target him, and go to a room above which is uninhabited and pick pocket him that way.  I personally just walked up behind him made 2 attempts and got it, not before needing a rez cuz i didnt realize i would be KoS in Neriak.  One reason that you may be KoS is your deity btw, no matter what form you are in.<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br>~Tactikal Mizkalculation~&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>60 ASSASSIN <br>Cruxor Thunderblade<br>Level 51 gimp Paladin<br>Vazaelle<br></td></tr>
